query:
SELECT 
  id,
  project_id,
  status,
  started_at,
  completed_at,
  paused_at,
  error_message,
  TIMESTAMPDIFF(MINUTE, started_at, COALESCE(paused_at, completed_at, NOW())) as duracao_minutos
FROM enrichment_runs
ORDER BY id DESC
LIMIT 5;
